snippet: LEAD: An aftershock of last month's deadly earthquake jolted Northern California on Wednesday night, but the authorities said today that the only harm appeared to be more jangled nerves....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: An aftershock of last month's deadly earthquake jolted Northern California on Wednesday night, but the authorities said today that the only harm appeared to be more jangled nerves.

headline.main: No Damage but Jarred Nerves From Aftershock in California
